# Project Context

You are adding a light/dark theme toggle to a vanilla HTML/CSS/JS word puzzle game (Daily Addicted). There is no build system — just static files served directly.

## Files to modify

- `css/style.css` — Theme variables and hardcoded color conversion
- `index.html` — Toggle button in header, theme.js script tag
- `js/theme.js` — New file for theme logic

