## HTML Changes

Replace the `.header-spacer` div in the header with a theme toggle button:

```html
<button id="theme-toggle" class="header-btn" aria-label="Switch to light mode" title="Switch theme">
  <svg id="theme-icon-dark" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="hidden">
